data.description: This stunning home is nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac. This spacious updated home features 4 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms.  The updated kitchen has a sleek electric range, stainless steel appliances, wine fridge as well as an indoor grill. The bright skylights provides plenty of light and adds to the charm of the home. The one-of-a -kind master suite is truly breathtaking and will be the perfect retreat to unwind after a long day. Allow your gatherings to overflow into the formal room that showcases custom bookshelves and display cabinets. You do not want to miss this well maintained and move in ready home. Call your favorite realtor to schedule a showing today.
